overview:
RPU is a mac and pc computer repair company in Miami, Fl.

RPU offers services such as laptop motherboard repair, laptop screen repair, laptop video chipset repair, laptop dc jack repair, mac logic board repair, mac water damage repair, mac glass screen repair, mac laptop screen repair, mac optical drive repair, and more. RPU also sells computer parts such as laptop chargers, laptop batteries, laptop screens, and laptop keyboards. RPU carries everything in stock, so your computer can be repaired faster. Less waiting, means you get your computer back in no time. RPU supplies 90% of all the computer repair shops in Miami, Fl.

When you want speedy fast computer repair, you go to RPU. RPU is located in Miami, FL, and has same day repair services available.

To contact RPU go to www.gorpu.com or call them at 786-371-8682
